videos.description: Brian Lewerke drops back, throws into the end zone and is picked off by Dasmond Tautalatasi.
videos.headline: Arizona St. comes up with clutch INT in end zone

videos.description: Brian Lewerke lofts a pass to Cody White who hauls it in for a 31-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Lewerke connects with White for 1st Michigan State TD

videos.description: Manny Wilkins throws a 27-yard fade to N'Keal Harry for Arizona State's first touchdown against Michigan State.
videos.headline: Harry hauls in 27-yard Arizona State TD

videos.description: Arizona State kicker Brandon Ruiz nails a 28-yard field goal as time expires to give Arizona State the upset win over Michigan State.
videos.headline: Arizona State upsets Michigan State with 28-yard field goal

videos.description: Herm Edwards is impressed with his Arizona State team's resiliency and applauds N'Keal Harry for making big plays.
videos.headline: Herm: Harry 'came up big' for win
